# Force LF line endings on checkout for every text file, on every platform.
# A CRLF shell script fails to run on Linux (a seedbox clone hit exactly this), and
# a CRLF shebang can break too — so pin LF and a checkout machine's git `autocrlf`
# setting can no longer mangle the scripts.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
